    "Additionally, it was found that filtering sub-graphs, which had been pointed out as a challenge in IR methods [10], can be performed on LLMs without requiring any special training.",
    "C. Limitation and future worksThis study has three major limitations.",
    "The first is the inadequacy of the sub-graph extraction method.",
    "In the context of failure events, chains of events are crucial, but this study extracts only one-hop chain.",
    "Future work should explore the introduction of an algorithm that can extract multi-hop chains."
